attributes.title: Horrid
attributes.review: I downloaded this app with high hopes in support of making America great again 🇵🇷🇵🇷but the app took 69 years to download and once it did download, when I opened the app it crashed and the second time I tried to open it, my entire phone broke 😱😱so I went to the apple store and got a new phone, the app was on that phone too and then when I tried to delete it, it wouldn’t work and broke that phone too, when I went back to the store I got an android and the app appeared again, so I got a flip phone and now it’s back, needless to say, I am now Amish 🙏

attributes.title: Dump the trump
attributes.review: Hello,Donald j trump I would Like to say I was a supporter of you before I got this app,I downloaded it in hopes of seeing the great famous Cheese puff but the app took a whole week to download.I never got to see your face 😢,once the app finally downloaded I opened it and it asked me to put my phone number so I did sadly it didn’t work.then my iPhone 11 crashed and wasn’t working for a whole month. I have already burned your trump 2020 flag,make America great again hate,and all my trump Kerch you have disappointed me cheese puff and I will no longer support you and your  racist way.

attributes.title: My DOG DIED because of this APP
attributes.review:
One morning my father woke up very early like two hours earlier than he normally does wake up.Anyways he turned on the Trump app as he was walking downstairs then some flashing lights took him by surprise my father started falling down the stairs and once he got to the bottom he landed on my dog which was a pug
So when my dad landed on the pug by accident the pug was just laying there motionless my dad started screaming and woke me my siblings and my mom up we quickly brought the pug to the vet and the vet said he was DEAD that’s all I really have to say I’m really sad right now 😭😥😭😥
